  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394590/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1765018663\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394590/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1765018663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394590/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1765018663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>The world is looking for a new hero!<br><br>Just Survive is an indie-action game in which all the tactics of a real soldier are applied. Parachuting will seem like a normal thing to you the more often you do it. Your mission is to clear the area of enemies and turn it into a peaceful one. <br><br>Act as quickly as possible because the chopper is waiting for you to fly to another conflict zone. Ready ?<br><br>Game Features :<br>- Multiple missions<br>- Driving Skills<br>- Limited ammo & life",
  "about_the_game": "The world is looking for a new hero!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nJust Survive is an indie-action game in which all the tactics of a real soldier are applied. Parachuting will seem like a normal thing to you the more often you do it. Your mission is to clear the area of enemies and turn it into a peaceful one. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nAct as quickly as possible because the chopper is waiting for you to fly to another conflict zone. Ready ?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame Features :<br />\r\n- Multiple missions<br />\r\n- Driving Skills<br />\r\n- Limited ammo & life",
